name: toyshi Hidden Camera Detectors - Hidden Devices Detector, Bug Detector, Anti Spy Detector, GPS Tracker & Listening Device Jammer, Hidden Camera Detector for Home Office Auto and Travel
feature_bullets: Privacy Protector - Feel safer with your hidden device detector! It can quickly and accurately detect eavesdropping devices, pinhole cameras, wired and wireless hidden cameras, GPS locators, etc. You can easily protect your privacy in public bathrooms, hotels, business meetings.,Signal Detection - Anti-spy bug detector can detect radio waves, 2G, 3G, 4G mobile signals, SIM card bug, magnetic field signal and various eavesdropper radio frequencies. Frequency detection range 1Mhz - 6.5Ghz. Innovative design and upgraded chip allow you to much more accurately find the signal source.,High Sensitivity - Hidden device detector uses an upgraded ultra-sensitive chip, and has 12 levels of sensitivity, allowing you to quickly and accurately find the signal source. The operation is simple, and the sensitivity can be adjusted according to actual needs with only one knob.,Multiple Mode - This product offers 4 modes: RF Wireless Signal Detection, UG Magnetic Field Signal Detection, Hidden Camera Detection, Flashlight Auxiliary Lighting.,Portable Design - Its compact size and lightweight, it can be easily carried to various occasions. You can take it on travels, business meetings ect. The super-long battery life provides 5-25 hours for continuous working and 5-7 days for standby, no worry about battery replacement or frequent battery charging.

name: Toiauaha 4K Digital Camera, 48MP Point and Shoot Camera for Kids, Teens, Beginners, 16X Digital Zoom, Auto Focus Vlogging Camera, 2.8 inch Screen, 2 Batteries, 32GB SD Card (Black)
feature_bullets: 【4K Digital Camera】This digital camera for kids supports JPG image resolution up to 48 megapixels and 4K (30FPS) MP4 video resolution, helping you record your most exciting moments with stunning images or videos. Plus, this vlogging camera comes with a 32GB SD card, so you don't need to worry about storage when you receive the camera.,【Vlogging Camera】 This vlogging camera supports auto focus (focus range: 0.5 feet to 3.3 feet), you don't need to buy a macro lens to take close-up shots of objects. All you need to do is press the capture button to focus this compact digital camera, then press the capture button again to capture a photo or video.,【Video Camera as Webcam】 This 4k video camera can be used as a webcam, connect to PC via USB cable, select "Camera Mode" to enjoy video chat on Facebook, YouTube, Skype or live broadcast on other social media. This compact digital camera supports an external 1/4" standard size tripod (not included),【Long Battery Life Camera】The digital camera is equipped with two 1200mAh rechargeable batteries. A fully charged battery can use 1-1.5H. And the camera also supports recording while charging. So you don't have to worry about running out of battery.,【Multifunctional 4K Digital Camera】This 16x digital camera supports time-lapse recording, Selfie, continuous shooting, fill light, date stamp and more. This camera is designed for amateurs, not professionals. Simple and convenient operation makes it an ideal gift for beginners, children, teenagers, students, the elderly.

Pet camera with 4 pcs IR lights; You can see every move of your baby or pet at night.,【Smart Tracking & Human Detection】Mubview indoor security cameras for home automatically track the motion if it detects motion. name: Hidden Security Cameras HUOMU Mini spy cam 1080P HD Wireless WiFi Remote View Tiny Home Surveillance Cameras Indoor Outdoor Video Recorder Smart Motion Detection
feature_bullets: ◆ This HUOMU hidden camera is a wide-angle hidden camera with a smaller size. The 1080P and 150-degree wide-angle lens captures details clearly and gives you a larger field of view. With its excellent structural design, it can simply be hidden anywhere in your home or office as long as you leave 1 x 0.6 inches (approx. 2.5 x 1.5 cm) of headroom.,◆ WIFI connection and button control dual operation mode: This smart camera can be controlled remotely via Android and iOS. Or if you don't want to use the app and WiFi connection, just press the button on the camera to record and take pictures. The device supports micro memory cards up to 128GB (not included). Built-in rechargeable 520mAh battery allows at least 1.5 hours of continuous video recording when fully charged, or you can connect it to a power source for immediate use.,◆ Easy-to-use multifunctional app: Although the camera is small, it is equipped with all the practical functions needed for a WIFI mini camera, just download the app on your iPhone or Android phone and configure the router Wi-Fi (2.4GHz only) , you can view live video remotely on the app from anywhere in the world, dynamic alarms, playback/snapshots/remote recording, iOS and Android compatible, SD card recording. Free app, one app with multiple cameras, multiple users with one camera, etc.,◆ Excellent IR Night Vision: Night vision is important for surveillance cameras that work around the clock, this camera has built-in 4 night vision IR LED lights to clearly see faces and details even in complete darkness (Note: Night vision needs to be turned on in the app).,◆ Smart Motion Detection Instant Alert: When the camera detects a moving object, it will immediately send an alert notification to the phone. 3 photos are captured and transferred back to the app, while the recorded video will be stored on the memory card at the same time (note: needs to be set in the app).

name: 4K Digital Camera for Photography 16X Zoom Anti-Shake Vlogging Camera with Flash 48MP Video AutoFocus Camera with 180°Flip Screen Compact Travel Camera with 2 Batteries 32GB Memory Card for Beginner
feature_bullets: 【UHD 4K & 48MP Digital Camera】The photography camera can capture 48 MP images and record 4K videos. The ultra-clear 3-inch screen supports 180-degree rotation, making it easy for selfies. The digital camera supports 16x digital zoom, which supports photography beginners‘ requirements. Compared to traditional cameras, it adds selfie, video pause function, recording while charging, slow-motion recording, and continuous shooting.,【Autofocus Function Upgrade】This digital camera has an autofocus function. When in photo mode, gently press the shutter button to keep the camera steady. The camera will automatically focus at this point. When you see the focus frame on the screen change from yellow to green, it means the focus is complete, and then press the shutter button firmly to take the current photo.,【Webcam and HDMI Function】This camera photo camera can be used as a PC camera, select the "Camera mode" by connecting to a computer to enjoy video chats on Skype or live streaming on social media such as Facebook and YouTube.,【Pause & Recording while Charging】This 4K photo camera has a convenient pause function that allows users to continue recording in the same file without starting a new one. This video camera comes with 2x800mAh lithium-ion battery and supports recording while charging, so you can connect it to AC or a power bank to charge it for continuous operation.,【Ideal Gift for Photography Beginners】This compact camera with a size of 5×3×2 (IN) is so lightweight and portable, comes with a 32GB memory card and an extra battery for worry-free photo-taking. Designed with amateurs in mind, its simple and convenient operation makes it an ideal gift for beginners, kids, teenagers, students, and elderly people who are interested in photography and filming.

name: eufy security Solo IndoorCam C24, 2K Security Indoor Camera, Plug-in Camera with Wi-Fi, IP Camera, Human & Pet AI, Voice Assistant Compatibility, Night Vision, Two-Way Audio, HomeBase not Compatible
feature_bullets: Relevant Recordings: The on-device AI determines whether a human or pet is present and only records when an event of interest occurs.,The Key is in the Detail: View every event in up to 2K clarity (1080P while using HomeKit) so you see exactly what is happening inside your home.,Communicate From Your Camera: Speak in real-time to anyone who passes via the camera’s built-in two-way audio.,Smart Integration: Connect your IndoorCam to Apple HomeKit (download our HomeKit user guide in the product information section below), the Google Assistant, or Amazon Alexa for complete control over your surveillance.,Sight at Night: Advanced night vision allows you to keep an eye on any room, even in low light settings.

name: Certified Refurbished Blink Mini – Compact indoor plug-in smart security camera, 1080 HD video, night vision, motion detection, two-way audio, Works with Alexa – 2 cameras
feature_bullets: A Certified Refurbished Blink Mini is refurbished, tested, and certified to look and work like new and comes with the same limited warranty as a new device. Certified Refurbished Amazon devices may be packaged in generic Amazon-branded boxes.,1080P HD indoor, plug-in security camera with motion detection and two way audio that lets you monitor the inside of your home day and night.,Get alerts on your smartphone whenever motion is detected or customize motion detection zones so you can see what matters most.,Store events conveniently and securely in the cloud with a 30-day free trial of the Blink Subscription Plan or locally with the Sync Module 2 and a USB flash drive (USB sold separately).,See, hear, and speak to people and pets in your home on your smartphone with Blink Mini’s live view and two-way audio features (live view is not continuous).,Sets up in minutes – just plug in the camera, connect it to wifi, and add it to your Blink app.,For additional ease of use, pair Blink Mini with a supported Alexa-enabled device to engage live view, and arm and disarm your camera, and more using just your voice.

name: Imou Indoor Security Camera 1080p WiFi Camera (2.4G Only) 360 Degree Home Camera with App, Night Vision, 2-Way Audio, Human Detection, Motion Tracking, Sound Detection, Local & Cloud Storage
feature_bullets: 1080P FHD & NIGHT VISION: 1080p full HD security camera provides crystal clear videos and recordings. Quality infrared LEDs extend the range of night vision reach up to 33 ft, lets you see everything clearly even in the dark,360°VIEW: 0 to 355°horizontal & -5 to 80°vertical rotation range creates a complete 360°coverage. With Imou Life App you can create a panorama and rotate the camera to view every corner of your home,HUMAN DETECTION & SMART TRACKING: quickly finds human targets and immediately sends a notification to you. Smart Tracking function makes the camera follows moving objects, records real-time videos and sends instant alerts to you. Scare unwelcome strangers away with built-in siren,2-WAY AUDIO & SOUND DETECTION: Interact with your pets and family with built-in speaker and microphone. Instant notification will be sent to you when the baby monitor detects baby crying, dog barking, or other abnormal sounds, keeping you aware of what's going on at home,EASY USE: Installation is easy. Via the user-friendly app, you can check the images & videos which are securely stored on a Micro SD card (up to 256GB) or the Imou Cloud, enable privacy mode, adjust detection sensitivity and region, set alarm schedule

name: Panasonic LUMIX FZ80 4K Digital Camera, 18.1 Megapixel Video Camera, 60X Zoom DC VARIO 20-1200mm Lens, F2.8-5.9 Aperture, Power O.I.S. Stabilization, Touch Enabled 3-Inch LCD, Wi-Fi, DC-FZ80K (Black)
feature_bullets: Point and Shoot Long Zoom Camera: 18.1 megapixel MOS sensor plus 60X zooms DC Vario lens (20 1220 millimeter and Power O.I.S. (Optical Image Stabilizer) captures far off moments,High Resolution View Finder and LCD Display: High resolution 1,170K dot view finder and rear touch enabled 3 inch LCD Display (1040 dots) are clear even in bright sunlight. Lens:14 elements in 12 groups,4K video Capture: 4K QFHD video recording (3840 x 2160) with three unique 4K ultra HD video pause and save 4K photo modes extracts individual high resolution Photos from 4K ultra HD video filmed at 30 frames per second to capture split second moments,Low Light Performance: Low light capture lets you enjoy photography during your nightlife again with impressive results; Note: Refer to user manual PDF attached below in technical specification for trouble shooting steps are on page 54,USB Charging and Wi-Fi Connectivity: Enjoy travel ready technologies like USB charging and Wi Fi connectivity to your mobile device; HDMI D (Micro), Micro USB and USB 2.0 provide additional connectivity to your favorite devices; Max resolution: 4896 x 3672,Viewfinder: 0.20" LVF (Live View Finder) (1,166k dots equiv.), Field of View: Approx. 100%, Lens 19.6x

name: WYZE Cam OG Indoor/Outdoor 1080p Wi-Fi Security Camera with Color Night Vision, Built-in Spotlight, 2-Way Audio, Compatible with Alexa & Google Assistant Cam Plus 3 Month Subscription
feature_bullets: Livestream with Color Night Vision - Monitor your home day or night with 1080P HD video & color night vision.,Indoor/Outdoor - Wyze Cam OG is a wired video camera with an IP65 rating so you can confidently install it outside in the rain or inside in the kids’ room. Wyze Outdoor Power Adapter (sold separately) required for outdoor use.,Motion/Sound Notifications - Wyze Cam OG alerts you instantly when motion or sound is detected. Motion Detection Zones and custom settings allow you to adjust the sensitivity of detection or turn it off completely,Easy to set up: Plug it in, power it up, and complete setup through the Wyze app. Then the included 3 months of Cam Plus is automatically activated with an optional renewal.,Never miss a moment: Cam Plus records unlimited full motion whenever it’s detected. Feel more secure knowing your Wyze Cam with free 3 months Cam Plus will capture the full story.,Smarter alerts: Wyze Cams come with motion detection alerts, but they can’t detect people, packages, pets, or vehicles. Cam Plus gives you the option to only receive alerts of your interest, which can reduce notifications by up to 70%.

name: Doorbell Camera,Wireless Video doorbell, tenants Offices,Waterproof doorbell, Anti-Theft Video doorbell, Suitable for Houses, Apartments, no Drilling
feature_bullets: 【Internet Smart Doorbell Camera】This wireless doorbell camera is perfect for smart home security. It has the function of mobile phone video call, voice-changing intercom, and automatic capture function. Plus, it has a long standby time.,【Clear Infrared Night Vision】The combination of full HD resolution of the doorbell camera and ultra-wide-angle lens enables the doorbell to record clearly. It also performs equally well in night vision mode. Viewing distance is 16 feet in total darkness with no light pollution.,【Multifunctional Smart】This camera is small and compact. Video intercom, camera, cloud storage, group sharing, compatible with iOS and Android, making your home safer and life more convenient. Night vision so you can get home safely even at night.,【Timely notification for snapping】Press the doorbell to snap a photo. If no one answers, the photo will be uploaded to the history record and a notification will be sent to your mobile phone. You can view or download it to your mobile phone at any time. Once human motion is detected. Quick alerts are also sent to your phone. The noise-canceling microphone and speaker system built into the camera provides two-way high-fidelity conversations at all times.,【Rechargeable Battery & IP65 Waterproof】: The video doorbell is equipped with 2 large-capacity rechargeable batteries, each time the battery runs out, you can continue to use it after fully charging, which is environmentally friendly and saves money. To ensure your protection lasts 24/7, we use an IP65 waterproof design. Safe to use in all weather conditions.

name: eufy security S220 Indoor Cam, 2K, Pan & Tilt, Indoor Security Camera, Wi-Fi Plug-in Camera, Human & Pet AI, Voice Assistant Compatibility, Night Vision, Motion Tracking, HomeBase Compatible
feature_bullets: Relevant Recordings: The on-device AI determines whether a human or pet is present and only records when an event of interest occurs.,The Key is in the Detail: View every event in up to 2K clarity (1080P while using HomeKit) so you see exactly what is happening inside your home.,Smart Integration: Connect your IndoorCam to Apple HomeKit (download our HomeKit User guide in the product information section below), the Google Assistant, or Amazon Alexa for complete control over your surveillance.,Follows the Action: When motion is detected the camera automatically tracks and follows the moving object. Pan the lens 360° horizontally or tilt it 96° vertically to get a clear view of the whole room.,Communicate From Your Camera: Speak in real-time to anyone who passes via the camera’s built-in two-way audio.

name: Digital Camera for Kids, Lecran 1080P 44MP Kids Camera with 32GB Card Point and Shoot Camera with 16X Zoom, Compact Portable Cameras Christmas Birthday Gift for Children Kids Teens Girl Boy(Black)
feature_bullets: Meaningful Gift: This digital camera for kids is equipped with a high-level CMOS Sensor and anti-shake function, which helps to capture vivid clear 44MP Images and record stable smooth FHD 1080P resolution videos. It's a meaningful gift for kids to cultivate their interest in photography, experience the lovely life, and leave funny memorable moments with family or friends.,Mini-Size & Easy to Use: Special mini-size design for kids to easily handheld, this point-and-shoot camera is small and lightweight, fits in kids' hands perfectly. Comes with a lanyard hang, portable for them to carry and move. And the clear simple settings and features of the camera make it easy for them to figure out and use themself.,Safe Materials & Creative Filters: Made of high-grade and eco-friendly reliable materials, the kid camera is safe and non-toxic, durable and withstands drops. This camera also supports six cute filter effects to choose from, kids could create more adorable colorful pictures.,Long Playtime & Multifunction: With two powerful rechargeable batteries, you can record up to 180 min videos on a single charge. The multifunctional digital camera also supports time stamp, 16X zoom, time-lapse, slow motion, continuous shoot, motion detection, face detection, self-timer, webcam, playback on computer or camera, etc.,Warranty & Package List: We provide a one-year satisfaction warranty, along with a no-hassle replacement policy, any problem or question, please contact us for help. Package list: Kid Camera, 32 GB SD Card, Type C Cable, Charger Adapter, 2 Batteries, Lanyard, and Bag.

name: Meeting Owl 3 (Next Gen) 360-Degree, 1080p HD Smart Video Conference Camera, Microphone, and Speaker (Automatic Speaker Focus & Smart Zooming)
feature_bullets: BETTER COLLABORATION. The Meeting Owl 3 captures 360° video in 1080p HD and 360° audio up to 18’ (5.5m). Automatically focuses on whoever is speaking to foster active collaboration and increased participation, while showing a 360° view of the room.,PLUG AND PLAY SIMPLICITY. Go from unboxing to your first meeting in <7 min. Simply plug in the power and USB, launch your preferred video conferencing platform, and start your meeting. Easily manage meetings through desktop, mobile or tablet apps.,UNIVERSALLY COMPATIBLE. Compatible with virtually all web-based video conferencing platforms, including Zoom, GoToMeeting, Google Meet, Microsoft Teams, Cisco Webex, BlueJeans, and many others.,SMARTER OVER TIME. Features the newest Owl Intelligence SystemTM, which focuses on people 4x faster. WiFI-enabled to get software upgrades and enhancements delivered over-the-air.,ADAPTS TO ANY SPACE. Pair two Meeting Owls or add an Expansion Mic to expand video and audio reach in larger spaces. Compatible with Owl Labs’ Whiteboard Owl and Meeting HQ to complete your hybrid room setup.

In camera mode, you can use the camera to automatically control focus. A focus mark frame will appear on the monitor, allowing the camera to focus at the exact moment you want to capture your subject.,📸【Pause Function & 16X Digital Zoom】 📸 Our digital camera supports 16x digital zoom, zoom can be achieved in the details of distant shots. This mini camera also has a pause function, you can pause while recording or playing video by pressing the "OK button". The built-in fill light can help you take high-quality photos in the dark.,📸【Webcam function & 2.8 inch IPS screen】📸 The digital camera can be used as a webcam. Two 700mAh large capacity batteries are included, has longer battery life, and is convenient for you to replace the battery and keep the camera powered up at any time. Small and light, easy to carry, you can shoot while charging.,📸【Multifunction & Best Gift】📸 This digital camera supports multifunction, the digital camera is a webcam, face detection, smile capture, continuous shooting, selfie, beauty function, shutter balance, auto close etc.This compact camera is the best gift for kids,teenagers,beginners and the elderly. name: KOMERY Camcorders Video Camera 4K 56MP UHD Video Camera for YouTube with External Mic Video Camera Camcorder with 32G SD Card 2.4G Remote IR Night Vision, 18X Digital Zoom Camcorder WiFi
feature_bullets: 【 User Friendly】Put the battery and SD card in this 4k video camera, then you can start to record or take pictures.,【Small and Lightweight】The digital video camera with a small size, comes with 3 batteries. It is easy to carry and can use for a long time when you are on vacation and to record all the beautiful things.,【 Supports Live Streaming】This camcorder can also use as a youtube camera. Connect it to the computer, then you can broadcast live on Facebook, Youtube, etc.,【2.4G Remote Control】This vlogging camera for youtube uses the newest 2.4G remote control technology, you can control it from all views, even you install the lens hood.,【Standard 4K High Quality】This UHD video camera with standard 4K 3840 × 2160 30FPS resolution for videos, and 56MP for pictures（Default is 24 MP）.,【IR Night Vision】This 4k camcorder with built-in infrared light, it will do great for capturing the family game night, or use for a self-facing vlog.,【About the lasting time of the battery】Some customers said the battery can only last 10 minutes, this only happens that they didn't charge the battery for the first time use. Please fully charge the battery first use.,【About formatting SD card】Please format the SD card for first use. Here is how: Press MENU, then press the W/T button to get into the Setup page, then Page down to find the Format function on the second page, press OK. The format is done.,【About the camcorder can't record consistently】All the SD cards use the FAT32 format. But there is a feature of FAT32 format: A single FAT32 file cannot exceed 4G, otherwise, it can't be read. The reason for the camcorder would not consistently record is not up to the camcorder, but the SD card format.,【How to get high quality pictures or videos】The three variables that matter the most in photography: light, subject, and composition, so when you test the video camera, please make sure there are enough light.

name: AOSU 2K Security Camera Indoor, Baby Monitor Pet Camera 360-Degree for Home Security, WiFi Camera with 5/2.4 GHz Wi-Fi, One-Touch Calls, Smart Motion Tracking, IR Night Vision, Compatible with Alexa
feature_bullets: 【One-Touch Calls】--- aosu home security cameras not only provide high-quality two-way audio, but also provide touch-to-talk. When your kids and aged people need help, they can press the phone button on the Aosu indoor camera to get talk with you instantly.,【5GHz/2.4GHz WiFi】--- Indoor security camera supports 5GHz/2.4GHz WiFi, you can easily install your own home security camera system. No subscription fee required.,【Smart Auto Track】--- Indoor security camera has automatic tracking function, when motion is detected, 360 degree security camera will automatically track and follow moving objects; and record the moving objects.,【360 Degree Round-Look】--- 360 degree camera can rotate 360° horizontally and tilt 155° vertically to get a clear view of the whole room. The 360 degree round-look function can record important places in the room, you can easily and quickly check the places you want to see.,【2K QHD Pet Camera & Compatible with Alexa】--- Home camera with 2K QHD resolution shows crystal clear and smooth live video and compatible with Alexa to let Alexa show your baby room, or any other room you have aosu baby monitor.

name: FOAOOD Security Cameras Wireless Outdoor with Solar Panel Cameras for Home Security, Home Camera with Color Night Vision, PIR Human Detection, 2-Way Talk, IP66 Waterproof, SD Card/Cloud Storage
feature_bullets: 【Solar Charging & 5000mAh Built-in Battery】FOAOOD wireless security camera solar panel adopts a concave-convex particle surface design, which can improve the photoelectric conversion efficiency by 20%, only need 2 hours of sunlight a day to maintain 365 days of uninterrupted protection of your family, no need to remove it to charge. The trouble of charging the camera. Even without the sun, the 5000mAh battery capacity can keep it running for 1-3 months.,【Color Night Vision & 1080P FHD Image】This WiFi camera adopts the latest floodlight design, with two more 45-lumen floodlights than other cameras, which can provide higher-definition full-color night vision and comprehensively improve the night vision effect; in addition, due to the design of the floodlight, The camera can also provide audible and visual alarms, with dazzling lights and a piercing alarm sound when someone breaks into your yard; driving away intruders.,【PIR Alarm & Optional Alarm Zone】DF220 outdoor security camera has PIR human body infrared detection, which can effectively reduce false alarms caused by insect pests, leaves, rain and snow, etc.; optional alarm area, only alarm the area you care about. When the camera detects motion, it will also send you a message in time to remind you what happened. Become a loyal guardian of your home, so that you no longer need to worry about accidents at home.,【IP66 Weatherproof & Multifunction】Our surveillance camera is made of high molecular polyester material, which can well resist all kinds of bad weather and protect your family at all times. In addition, the camera also has a two-way talk function, which allows you to talk directly to the person under the camera. Share with your family, view multiple cameras at the same time, keep an eye on who or what is important.,【Reliable Products & Customer Satisfaction Service】The product provides a one-year warranty service, you can buy with confidence. We adhere to the principle of customer first and serve customers wholeheartedly. If you encounter any problems during use, please feel free to contact us. FOAOOD will provide you with timely and professional technical support and provide you with a satisfactory solution.

name: Ring Stick Up Cam Solar HD security camera with two-way talk, Works with Alexa - White
feature_bullets: See, hear and speak to people from your phone, tablet or select Echo device with Stick Up Cam Solar, a solar-powered camera that brings peace of mind rain or shine. Includes privacy features, such as customizable privacy zones and audio privacy, to focus only on what's relevant to you.,With Live View, you can check in on your home any time through the Ring app.,With a Ring Protect Plan (subscription sold separately), record all your videos, review what you missed for up to 180 days, and share videos and photos.,Place on a flat surface or mount to a wall with the versatile mounting bracket. Add-on the Mount for Stick Up Cam (sold separately) for ceiling mount.,Watch over your entire home by connecting one or multiple Stick Up Cams to all your Ring devices in the Ring app.,Easily setup Stick Up Cam Solar by plugging-in the solar panel and connecting to Wi-Fi.,For added peace of mind, pair with Alexa to help you keep an eye on your home.

name: Double Din Car Stereo with Dash Cam - Voice Control Carplay, Android Auto, Steering Wheel Controls, 7" HD Touchscreen, Backup Camera, Bluetooth, Mirror Link, Subw, USB/TF/AUX, AM/FM Car Radio Receiver
feature_bullets: ✨Carplay&Android Auto: The double din car radio receiver support Apple CarPlay&Android Auto. You can making calls hands-free with the help of Siri/Google Assistant, easy to get phone contacts, emails, notifications, map navigation, music, videos and more which let you focus more on road safety while driving!,✨Backup Camera&Dash Cam: Supporting front/ rear camera, the A019 with a waterproof view and HD night vision AHD camera let you no longer worry about reversing safety, and display the image automatically when the vehicle shifts into reverse, working as a parking assistance. It comes with 150° wide angle lens, resolution with 1280*720P dash cam.( MicroSD card not included in dash cam, we recommend using a Sandisk Brand Class 10 Or Above, Max Support 32gb With Fat32 File System.),✨HD Touch Screen Multimedia Player: Equipped with 7 inch high definition capacitive touch screen and easily reachable physical buttons, USB, TF and AUX port to offer multiple options for music and movie enjoyment in the vehicle. Supporting 1920*1080P video, enhance your visual experience. You can put the mobile phone apps on the high-definition display via the mirror link that you could realize control between your phone and car stereo.,✨Dual Microphone Sound: Built-in microphone and external microphone interface, it can realize clear calls and accurate voice control in noisy environment, let you chat freely during the trip. Allowing you to enjoy high-quality audio stream and the music you like.,✨Double Check Your Car: Our car stereo is the U.S. standard size which compatible with most brands of car model, if you find that our stereo size does not match your dash size, please purchase a suitable dash kit, most brand dash kits use 173*98mm opening(Metra, PAC, Scosche dash kits, etc.)perfectly matching our car stereo, suitable for most cars and easy to install.,✨Important Tips: ①Please read our product size carefully in the picture, confirming that your dash size, factory wiring harness and radio antenna adapter are suitable before ordering, if not, you need to buy a special harness, dash kit, antenna adapter extra according to your car model. ②Please read the instructions before installation and contact us with any questions about the installation. ③The unit is not android system.,🎁Perfect gift for special day like birthday, holiday, Father's Day or Christmas, Thanksgiving Day.

name: 4K Digital Camera, 48MP Autofocus Video Camera with 3" 180°Flip Screen 32GB SD Card, 16X Digital Zoom, Compact Recorder Vlogging Cameras for YouTube with Built-in Mic, 2 Batteries for Beginners
feature_bullets: 📸【Advanced Autofocus Digital Camera】The digital cameras combined with advanced Autofocus technology and 48 Megapixels, help deliver clear images with precise enhanced details. Just press the shutter button halfway down to focus, and fully down to shoot an image after the focus frame on the screen turn green from yellow, then you will gain a vivid detailed macro image.,📸【UHD 4K Video Record & 3" Flip Screen】Feature with 4K High-Resolution and a built-in microphone, this digital camera for photography also has good performance in recording smooth sharp videos up to 4K Ultra HD resolution. And the 3" IPS LCD flip screen makes it easy to take perfect selfies or vlogs.,📸【Webcam Function & HDMI Connection】The 4K cameras can be used as a webcam, you can use it to live stream on Youtube or have a video chat with friends or family members. Support connecting the camera to the TV through an HDMI cable and playback the videos you took in 4K high definition. Comes with a 32GB SD card, two batteries, a camera charger, a charging cable, an HDMI cable, a lanyard, a manual, and a bag.,📸【Compact & Easy to Use】The slim stylish lightweight design makes the 4K video camera compact to carry and move, easy to bring on your adventures. And it's super easy to use and control, an ideal Christmas gift, birthday gift, or holiday gift for teens, kids, students, and beginners to learn photography and videography.,📩【Multi-Functions & Warranty】Additionally, the vlogging camera also supports 16X digital zoom, flashlight, anti-shake, playback function, pause function, time-lapse, self-timer, face detection, slow-motion, continuous shooting, anti-shake, and so on. We provide a one-year satisfaction warranty, along with a no-hassle replacement policy, any problem, please contact us for help.

name: 2Pack Security Cameras Outdoor Wireless,2K FHD Battery Powered Camera for Home Security, Cloud/SD(up to 256G), No Monthly Fee, AI Motion Detection, Color Night Vision,2-Way Audio, Works with Alexa
feature_bullets: 【3MP FHD Live Video and Full-Color Night Vision Security Camera】 These home security cameras offer a wide viewing angle of 110 degrees, with high-quality 2K video and image resolution. They feature two modes of night vision, including full-color night vision and infrared night vision with a visible range of up to 33ft. This allows you to easily identify important details such as faces or license plates even in low-light conditions. （Not support 5GHz WiFi.）,【100% Wire-Free and Rechargeable Battery WiFi Camera】 This indoor camera with low power consumption, it can provide worry-free use for 1 to 3 months on a single charge. You can install it anywhere without the need for any wires. Additionally, this outdoor camera with IP65 waterproof rating, making it suitable for any weather conditions outdoors. Installation is also simple, as you can easily remove or install the security cameras with the provided bracket. (only works with 2.4GHz WiFi),【Smart PIR Motion Detection and Instant Alerts】This wifi camera uses Infrared sensor technology and cloud image analysis to detect motion in real time. Equipped with AI PIR, it can detect human motion and send instant alerts to your smartphone. You can also customize detection zones to suit your home, ensuring that you only receive notifications for the areas you care about, reducing unwanted notifications and false alarms.And this security camera can be shared with multiple users.,【2-Way-Talk& Siren Alarm】For home security purposes, this outdoor camera is equipped with a siren alarm and spotlight, in addition to providing motion notifications. And you can customize your own siren alarm with messages like "Hey, I've called the police, please leave now." The camera also includes a high-quality two-way audio function that allows you to communicate with your family or guests from anywhere and at any time. Also, it can work with Alexa.,【No Subscriptions Fee】These home security cameras have two storage options: an SD card (up to 256GB) and cloud storage. It offers free rolling 3-day cycle cloud storage, allowing you to enjoy storage service without any subscription. Additionally, it provides a free trial of advanced features such as AI recognition and custom alert areas. After the free trial, the advanced features are available for as low as $2.99 per 15 days.

name: WonderFoto 1080P WiFi Camera, Spy Hidden Camera Detector, Security Camera with Motion Detection, Secret Cameras for Home, Dome Cameras for Surveillance
feature_bullets: 💫【2023 Latest Smart Model】 wireless WIFI camera features impressive 150° wide angle, 1080P live video at 25frames per second, motion activated push alerts, recording while charging, remote Playback/Snapshot/Recording, Live stream from anywhere in the world,💫【WiFi Connection Function】 With Wifi connectivity to room's router, you can watch live video feed or playbacks no matter where you are by accessing the APP(The app never charges),💫 【Cop Cameras with Night Vision】 This surveillance cameras built LED IR light and the infrared distance up to 16 feet, which captures every detail in low light or even in the dark.,💫【Security camera 】 Our camera has a round, making it very suitable as a home security camera. With camera , you can put the camera in the corner of a house, warehouse, backyard, shop, office, etc.,💫【Advanced Motion Detection Alerts】 The wireless camera will send push notification with images to your phone once motion is detected. You can log into the App to see what’s going on in real time and never worry about missing something important. This cam automatically records and overwrites the oldest SD card files when full for continuous recording.

name: Digital Camera 4K Auto Focus 48MP Vlogging Digital Video Camera for YouTube 32G Memory Card Portable Digital Camera with Viewfinder Built-in Flash Anti-Shake Rotary Button
feature_bullets: 📸【4K & 48MP Digital Camera】 With a 4K and 48-megapixel digital camera, you'll be able to capture stunning, high-resolution photos and videos. Whether you're an photographer or simply want to take higher-quality photos and videos of your everyday life, this camera delivers stunning results. With its powerful 48-megapixel sensor, you'll be able to capture even the smallest details with clarity, while its 4K video recording capability allows you to create crisp and clear videos that are perfect for sharing on social media or showcasing on a big screen.,📸【Autofocus Function】 The autofocus function on this digital camera makes it easy to capture sharp, clear images with minimal effort. This video camera's autofocus system is designed to ensure that your images are always in focus. With advanced autofocus algorithms, you'll be able to take stunning photos and videos with ease, even in low-light conditions.,📸【Fashionable Appearance Design】 The silver and black splicing design of this digital camera is both fashionable and atmospheric, making it the perfect accessory for anyone who wants to capture high-quality images while looking stylish. With its sleek, modern design, this camera is sure to turn heads and make a statement wherever you go. Plus, its lightweight, compact design makes it easy to take with you on the go, whether you're traveling to a new city or simply exploring your own backyard.,📸【Viewfinder Function】 The viewfinder function on this digital vlogging camera allows you to see exactly what you're capturing in real-time, making it easier to compose your shots and ensure that you're getting the perfect shot every time. Whether you're shooting in bright sunlight or low-light conditions, the viewfinder function helps you to see your subject clearly, so you can take the perfect photo or video with ease.,📸【Rotary Button, A Key to Switch Between Different Modes】 The rotary button on this digital camera makes it easy to switch between different modes, allowing you to customize your settings and capture the perfect image every time.With a simple twist of the rotary button, you can switch between multiple modes: Multi-Snapshot, Time-lapse Photo , Motion Detection,Anti-Shake.,📸【Built-in Flash and Anti-Shake】 Capture stunning, clear photos and videos every time with our top-of-the-line camera featuring a built-in flash and anti-shake function. Say goodbye to blurry or grainy images and hello to sharp, vibrant pictures in any lighting conditions. The advanced anti-shake function guarantees stable photos and smooth, jarring-free videos. With intuitive controls and a simple menu system, this camera is perfect for photographers of all levels.

name: wansview 2K Security Cameras Wireless Outdoor-2.4G WiFi Home Security Cameras via Remote Control with Phone APP for 360° View, Color Night Vision, 24/7 SD Card Storage, Works with Alexa/Google Home
feature_bullets: [ 2K Outdoor Camera with Full-Color Night Vision ] Compared with 1080P cameras, this waterproof outdoor camera has 2K 3MP pixels which show high-quality pictures. With the built-in white light, this outdoor security camera can display clear images even in extremely dark environments. When the light is turned on at night, it shows the color of night vision. So you can clearly see whether there are suspicious objects in the courtyard and see everything that happened within the scope of monitoring.,[ Motion Detection Triggers Real-Time Alerts ] This security outdoor camera has a built-in sensor. When you activate the motion alert in the Wansview Cloud app, the camera will start to record automatically once the motion is detected. And the Wansview cloud app will send you real-time push alerts about the motion, which highly ensures your home security in time.,[ 24/7 Recording Ensure Home Security ] This security outdoor camera supports motion alert, SD card storage, and cloud storage. It supports 24/7 continuous recording with an SD card (not included) so you will never miss any important moment. And cloud storage can be your backup storage, but it's not mandatory. Moreover, you can access the camera on different devices, create several family accounts, and share the camera with your family and friends. So the shared ones can also access the camera.,[ Two-Way Audio via the App ] This security outdoor camera is equipped with a built-in microphone & speaker that allows you to talk with your family or visitors through the App.When you are not at home, you can talk through the microphone to drive away uninvited guests, or talk to the other party on the camera side. Therefore, the W7 camera is an important security tool for your home security.,[ Service After Sales ] Wansview provides lifelong technical support and after-sales service to customers, please contact us if necessary. （The package contains camera*1, USB cable*1,plug *1,and installation guide*1,and packs of mounting screws*2). Additionally,it can work in rainy day, snowy day, and extreme weather since it's rated with IP65 waterproof（working temperature: -10℃ to 50℃).

name: eufy security S230 SoloCam S40, Solar-Powered, Wireless Outdoor Security Camera, Battery Camera, 2K Resolution, No Monthly Fee (Renewed)
feature_bullets: Forever Power, Solar Style: Sunlight each day is enough to continuously power SoloCam S40, so you never have to worry about changing the battery. And when the sun sets, the built-in battery keeps the juice flowing.,Light Up the Night: The ultra-bright 600-lumen spotlight switches on as soon as motion is detected, shining a light on any unwanted guests, while the color night vision picks out details in the darkness up to 8 meters away.,The Key is in the Detail: Capture every event that occurs around your home in ultra-clear 2K resolution.,No Hidden Costs: SoloCam is a one-time purchase. There are no monthly fees or hidden costs. Everything is done on-device for complete security and transparency.,Relevant Recordings: The built-in AI ensures SoloCam S40 only records when a person is present, rather than an animal.

name: eufy security S220 Indoor Cam, 2K, Pan & Tilt, Indoor Security Camera, Wi-Fi Plug-in Camera, Human & Pet AI, Voice Assistant Compatibility, Night Vision, Motion Tracking, HomeBase Compatible
feature_bullets: Relevant Recordings: The on-device AI determines whether a human or pet is present and only records when an event of interest occurs.,The Key is in the Detail: View every event in up to 2K clarity (1080P while using HomeKit) so you see exactly what is happening inside your home.,Smart Integration: Connect your IndoorCam to Apple HomeKit (download our HomeKit User guide in the product information section below), the Google Assistant, or Amazon Alexa for complete control over your surveillance.,Follows the Action: When motion is detected the camera automatically tracks and follows the moving object. Pan the lens 360° horizontally or tilt it 96° vertically to get a clear view of the whole room.,Communicate From Your Camera: Speak in real-time to anyone who passes via the camera’s built-in two-way audio.

name: Digital Camera for Kids, Lecran 1080P 44MP Kids Camera with 32GB Card Point and Shoot Camera with 16X Zoom, Compact Portable Cameras Christmas Birthday Gift for Children Kids Teens Girl Boy(Black)
feature_bullets: Meaningful Gift: This digital camera for kids is equipped with a high-level CMOS Sensor and anti-shake function, which helps to capture vivid clear 44MP Images and record stable smooth FHD 1080P resolution videos. It's a meaningful gift for kids to cultivate their interest in photography, experience the lovely life, and leave funny memorable moments with family or friends.,Mini-Size & Easy to Use: Special mini-size design for kids to easily handheld, this point-and-shoot camera is small and lightweight, fits in kids' hands perfectly. Comes with a lanyard hang, portable for them to carry and move. And the clear simple settings and features of the camera make it easy for them to figure out and use themself.,Safe Materials & Creative Filters: Made of high-grade and eco-friendly reliable materials, the kid camera is safe and non-toxic, durable and withstands drops. This camera also supports six cute filter effects to choose from, kids could create more adorable colorful pictures.,Long Playtime & Multifunction: With two powerful rechargeable batteries, you can record up to 180 min videos on a single charge. The multifunctional digital camera also supports time stamp, 16X zoom, time-lapse, slow motion, continuous shoot, motion detection, face detection, self-timer, webcam, playback on computer or camera, etc.,Warranty & Package List: We provide a one-year satisfaction warranty, along with a no-hassle replacement policy, any problem or question, please contact us for help. Package list: Kid Camera, 32 GB SD Card, Type C Cable, Charger Adapter, 2 Batteries, Lanyard, and Bag.

name: WonderFoto Wireless Camera WiFi Security Dog Body Small Detector Cameras,Pet Mini Home Nanny Cam with Babysitter Surveillance Camera,Indoor and Outdoor Cams Compatible with Android
feature_bullets: 💫【2023 Latest Smart Model】 wireless WIFI camera features impressive 150° wide angle, 1080P live video at 25frames per second, motion activated push alerts, recording while charging, remote Playback/Snapshot/Recording, Live stream from anywhere in the world,💫【WiFi Connection Function】 With Wifi connectivity to room's router, you can watch live video feed or playbacks no matter where you are by accessing the APP(The app never charges),💫 【Cop Cameras with Night Vision】 This surveillance cameras built LED IR light and the infrared distance up to 16 feet, which captures every detail in low light or even in the dark.,💫【Security camera 】 Our camera has a round, making it very suitable as a home security camera. With camera , you can put the camera in the corner of a house, warehouse, backyard, shop, office, etc.,💫【Advanced Motion Detection Alerts】 The wireless camera will send push notification with images to your phone once motion is detected. You can log into the App to see what’s going on in real time and never worry about missing something important. This cam automatically records and overwrites the oldest SD card files when full for continuous recording.

name: AOSU 2K Security Camera Indoor, Baby Monitor Pet Camera 360-Degree for Home Security, WiFi Camera with 5/2.4 GHz Wi-Fi, One-Touch Calls, Smart Motion Tracking, IR Night Vision, Compatible with Alexa
feature_bullets: 【One-Touch Calls】--- aosu home security cameras not only provide high-quality two-way audio, but also provide touch-to-talk. When your kids and aged people need help, they can press the phone button on the Aosu indoor camera to get talk with you instantly.,【5GHz/2.4GHz WiFi】--- Indoor security camera supports 5GHz/2.4GHz WiFi, you can easily install your own home security camera system. No subscription fee required.,【Smart Auto Track】--- Indoor security camera has automatic tracking function, when motion is detected, 360 degree security camera will automatically track and follow moving objects; and record the moving objects.,【360 Degree Round-Look】--- 360 degree camera can rotate 360° horizontally and tilt 155° vertically to get a clear view of the whole room. The 360 degree round-look function can record important places in the room, you can easily and quickly check the places you want to see.,【2K QHD Pet Camera & Compatible with Alexa】--- Home camera with 2K QHD resolution shows crystal clear and smooth live video and compatible with Alexa to let Alexa show your baby room, or any other room you have aosu baby monitor.

name: Apexcam Action Camera 4K Sports Camera 20MP 40M 170°Wide-Angle WiFi Waterproof Underwater Camera with 2.4G Remote Control 2 Batteries 2.0'' LCD Ultra HD Camera with Mounting Accessories Kit
feature_bullets: 📷Professional 4K Ultra HD Action Camera: Available in 4K / 30FPS, 2.7K / 30FPS, 1080P / 60FPS, 1080P / 30FPS, 720P / 60FPS and 720P / 120FPS video resolutions. With 16MP images and a 170° super wide-angle 6G fisheye lens,Capture and share your world in a fantastic resolution.,📷Wireless Wrist 2.4G Remote Control: Bring the remote control on your wrist, and install the action camera on the helmet or the place where it can't be touched. It is convenient to record the wonderful moment. The remote control wireless range is 15 meters (49 FT), and the remote control waterproof level IPX6 life waterproof, please do not immerse the remote control in the water.,📷2.0’’LCD WiFi Action Camera: Use APP/APK to keep and share your exciting sports moments on your phone or tablet, WiFi signal range up to 10M(33 FT), 2.0’’LCD HD display allows you to preview anytime, anywhere Wonderful videos and photos in motion.,📷130FT Waterproof Camera Free Accessories: Equipped with durable IP68 waterproof sleeve can dive 40 meters deep, ideal for swimming, diving, rafting, surfing and other water sports, this underwater camera is also equipped with 2 rechargeable 1050mAh battery and the battery charger can charge two batteries at the same time, very convenient to save time. And it comes with many other multi-functional accessories (most are compatible with gopro cameras).,📷Multi-Function Action Camera: Including loop recording, slow motion photography, driving mode, image flipping, time-lapse photo, exposure adjustment, white balance adjustment; You can take the camera to a variety of sports environments and use it, the effect will exceed your expectations.

name: Ring Stick Up Cam Battery HD security camera with custom privacy controls, Simple setup, Works with Alexa - Black
feature_bullets: See, hear and speak to people from your phone, tablet or select Echo device with Stick Up Cam Battery, a battery-powered camera that can be mounted indoor or out.,With Live View, you can check in on your home any time through the Ring app.,With a Ring Protect Plan (subscription sold separately), record all your videos, review what you missed for up to 180 days, and share videos and photos.,Place on a flat surface or mount to a wall with the versatile mounting bracket. Add-on the Mount for Stick Up Cam (sold separately) for ceiling mount.,Watch over your entire home by connecting one or multiple Stick Up Cams to all your Ring devices in the Ring app.,Easily setup Stick Up Cam Battery by inserting the battery pack and connecting to Wi-Fi.,For added peace of mind, pair with Alexa to help you keep an eye on your home.

name: senri Mini Security Camera, 1080P HD WiFi Home Indoor Outdoor Camera for Baby/Pet/Nanny, IP Camera Remote Viewing for Security with iOS,Android Phone APP
feature_bullets: [150°Wide-angle & 1080P HD] With 150° wide-angle lens and 1080P HD reselution, senri mini camera captures details clearly and provide you with a larger view of everything indoors. With its excellent structural design and the magnet, it can be easily hidden anywhere to watch your home, office, yard and etc.,[2022 Version WiFi Camera] senri mini wireless camera is the latest product in 2022, supports iOS and Android devices, download the APP and connect it to the network, you can view live video on the App from anywhere in the world. The video can be save in the micro SD card, you can view the material on phone, pad, computer.,[Video Recording 24/7 when charged] This spy camera contains high-quality rechargeable lithium-ion battery, which can last for about 120 min. And you can connect it to power bank or other USB ports to get a longer time recording, or connect to the power supply to achieve 24/7 continuously turning on.,[5m Infra-red Night Vision] Equipped with 6 invisible and non-luminous infrared lights, this mini camera provides a outstanding night view range up to 5m, perfect for your room’s day and night supervision. It can record 10m in the daytime.,[128GB SD Card Supported & Technical Support] senri mini camera support SD card from 2GB to 128GB( not included). And senri provides 30 days money back, 3 year technical support, if you have any problem about our cameras, contact us in time.

Supporting 16X Digital Zoom, besides, it upgraded to autofocus, tracking object automaticlly to capture clear photos, for close-up shoting, you can also half pressing the shutter for fast focusing.,[ Flip Screen & Pop-up Flashlight ] This vlog camera has a 3'' flip screen that can be rotated 180 degrees to meet your shooting needs in different poses and realize low-camera shooting, making selfie shooting easier and more fun. And its retractable flashlight system providing the best solution in dim light conditions. When your vision is limited in a dark environment, you can pop up the flash to get a brighter view.,[ Webcam for Live Streaming ] The small camera can be used as webcam by selecting the "PC Camera" mode after connected to your PC via the USB cable, you can have video calls or start live streaming to share things on social media. So its not only a photo camera for photography but also a streaming camera and video camera for Youtube, Instagram, etc.,[ Multifunctions Photography Camera with Accessories ] The video camera has multiple functions including time-lapse, slow-motion, looping video, self-timer, Continuous Shooting, flash and more. Moreover, this video recorder also contains multiple accessories such as mini tripod, Hot-shoe & threaded double head bracket, external video light (video light AAA batteries not included), and two rechargeable camera batteries.,[ Perfect Gift for Beginners ] The pocket camera has an exquisite looking, is perfect gift for entry-level users who just start in content creation. It is the very affordable vlog camera for creators, vloggers and streamers. Recording travel, sports events, weddings, birthday parties and other activities will be so easy with its help, is an ideal gift for friends, teens and families. name: Video Camera Camcorder Full HD 1080P 30FPS 24.0 MP IR Night Vision Vlogging Camera Recorder 3.0 Inch IPS Screen 16X Zoom Camcorders Remote Control with 2 Batteries
feature_bullets: ♥24MP & 1080P FHD CAMCORDER - This digital video camera supports shooting of Full HD 1080p(30FPS) video and 24MP photo. Besides, it supports 3.0 inch IPS screen, 16X digital zoom and remote control. All these configurations provide smooth shooting experience and wonderful effect. This camcorder is so sturdy and lightweight that you can take it around. In a word, it would be a perfect gift for your parents and kids.,♥IR NIGHT VISION & SUPPORT EXTERNAL MICROPHONE - Night vision camcorder can shoot high definition image and videos in low light condition and even in the darkness, additionally the video shoot camera is compatible with external fill light to complement the light source. It also supports the external microphone with 3.5mm jack for clear audio recording and expandable storage with an SD card up to 128GB. (Microphone, SD card and fill LED light are not included in the package.),♥WEBCAM – The vlogging camera can be connected the PC with USB cable. Then you can transfer your files to your computer by choosing “MSDC” or take it as a webcam by choosing the “PC CAM” mode so as to enjoy video chatting or live streaming.,♥PAUSE & REMOTE CONTROL - You can pause long video shooting at any point and continue from where you stopped without starting a new file. This camera also support remote control. Therefore, all the controls can be accessed through physical or remote controller buttons, no members are excluded from the group photo. This vlog camera supports recording while charging and also comes with two 1500mAh batteries so you don't worry about running out of power when you are recording an important event.,♥MULTIFUNCTION - This digital camcorder supports video at intervals, low-speed video，motion detection, time-lapse, self-shooting and continuous shooting. This lightweight, small and easy-to-use digital camcorder is equipped with high-class material and advanced technology, records high-quality image, and it's a perfect gift for friends, family members to record their special lovely moments and travel time!

name: IHOXTX Security Cameras Wireless Outdoor, Flood Light Solar Cameras for Home Security, Home Camera with Color Night Vision, PIR Human Detection, 2-Way Talk, IP66 Waterproof, SD Card/Cloud Storage
feature_bullets: ［Solar Camera with 5000mAh Built-in Battery] This surveillance camera has a built -in 5000mAh electricity, equipped with solar panels, so that it can maintain continuous electricity for 365 days. When there is a sun during the day, it can be charged for the camera. When there is no sun at night, use battery power to protect your family's safety. (Please note that solar panels need to be installed in a place where the solar is direct.),[2 Floodlights Color Night Vision] This WiFi camera equipped with 2 floodlights, gives you color night vision, capturing the image as good as the daytime, even at night. 1080P picture quality, providing you with HD images without taking up too much network, maintaining the smoothness of the video.,[Intelligent PIR Detection] DF220 outdoor safety camera has PIR human infrared detection, which can reduce false alarms caused by insects, leaves, rain, rain and snow. Only detect people to ensure that every message you receive is important news. In addition, you can also turn on the sound and light alarm. When the camera detects the action, it can also make sounds and flashes to expel the invaders.,[Multifunction Solar Camera] IP66: Our surveillance camera is made of high molecular polyester material, which can well resist all kinds of bad weather and protect your family at all times. 2 Way Talk: the camera also has a two-way talk function, which allows you to talk directly to the person under the camera. Share with your family, view multiple cameras at the same time, keep an eye on who or what is important.,[Reliable Products and Satisfied Service] We adhere to the principle of customer first and serve customers wholeheartedly. If you encounter any problems during use, please feel free to contact us. IHOXTX will provide you with timely and professional technical support and provide you with a satisfactory solution.

name: 2K Security Camera Outdoor Wireless WiFi with 360° PTZ, ZUMIMALL Battery Powered Wireless Cameras for Home Surveillance, Spotlight & Siren/PIR Detection/3MP Color Night Vision/2-Way Talk/IP66/Cloud/SD
feature_bullets: 【360° View Pan/Tilt Control & 2K/3MP Color Night Vision】 - Security cameras wireless outdoor can rotate its head 355° horizontally and 120° vertically. Simply controlling the mobile phone APP, you can remote 360° all-round monitoring to protect your property. Equipped with 4 infrared LEDs, 3MP FHD resolution (2560*1440), 130° viewing wide-angle, and 4X digital zoom, the outdoor camera wireless allows you to remotely shoot and watch up to 65ft range of Clear pictures and videos,【Newly Upgraded Rechargeable Battery & 100% Wireless & 2.4G WiFi】-Security camera battery powered update the defect of the old 15000 battery with poor battery life, Zumimall wireless outdoor wifi security camera built-in new version rechargeable battery, provide 3-8months of uninterrupted use. Best choice for sunless areas. With a 4dBi antenna, the outdoor cameras wireless can connect your 2.4G WiFi quickly from a farther distance. (Battery powered camera does not support 5GHz WiFi),【PIR Human Detection & Real-time Alerts & Spotlight & Siren】- Home security cameras using the latest AI algorithm and PIR sensor with can identify person, pet, vehicle, and parcel, support set alarm plan and adjust sensitivity level to minimize false alarms. Once motion detection is triggered, a notification will be sent to your mobile APP and the video or image will be stored in the SD card or cloud storage so that users can more accurately capture the content they care about in real-time.,【2-way Audio & DIY Detection Area & Multi-user Sharing】- Built-in microphone, Outdoor security cameras can custom and pre-set detection areas and interact online with children, guests, couriers, etc. If another user has the same "ZUMIMALL APP" as you, you can share the QR code with him and watch the wonderful content of the camera together. Outdoor cameras for home security are not only a medium for you to soothe your beloved pet remotely but also a defensive tool to scare off intruders.,【IP66 Waterproof & Wide Applicability】- The wireless cameras for home security have waterproof and dustproof housing to ensure it keeps working through any weather. The standard operating temperature of -13°F to 140°F (-25°C to 60°C ) can show excellent performance. One APP can add multiple Zumimall cameras to control. You can equip this outdoor security camera together anywhere in your home. Such as indoor/outdoor, yard, garage, shop, and other places.

name: Mini Wireless WiFi Camera HD 1080P Home Security Cameras with Feed Covert Baby Nanny Cam with Cell Phone App Tiny Smart Pet Dog Cameras with Night Vision and Motion Detection
feature_bullets: 【Newest Mini WiFi Camera】-This camera is the latest small size, wide-angle Wi-Fi camera with built-in magnet. With a 1080P full HD mini camera and a 150-degree wide-angle lens, the camera can capture details clearly, bringing you an unprecedented wide scene. The perfect surveillance camera with its compact size and prominent lens design allows you to easily and discreetly capture any lens in your home, office or car,[How to connect]- Before you use it, please charge it. 1. Download 365cam on your mobile phone. 2. Open the software, and then add the camera device through the APP.3.Choose connection way,the first AP connection(applying for direct connect). The second, AP distribution network(applying for remote monitoring), Connect to the home wifi and enter the password.4.Open the WIFI setting and find the ***DG0**or ***DOU***wifi hotspot, Connect and return to the app to check whether the device is online,【Excellent Nanny Camera】- camera only supports 2.4GHz router WiFi with password doesn't support 5Gwifi. Insert the micro sd card（NOT Included). We have detailed instructions to help you install more conveniently.Now you are ready to view real-time picture on the app remotely from anywhere in the world. As a nanny camera,With the help of the built-in magnet can be attached to any iron surface,[Record while charging]- This mini camera has a built-in high-quality rechargeable lithium-ion battery, which has a long battery life. In addition, the product has a snake tube data cable, you can connect it to the power supply or mobile power bank, adjust the angle of the data cable, it can charge and fix the camera while charging, keep working continuously without worrying about not being able to use it when it's out of power.,【Motion Detection And Night Vision Wireless Camera】-With upgraded smart motion detection, now you can manually set the sensor sensitivity. Once the motion is detected, the camera will send a push notification with the image to your phone. You can log in to the app at any time to see what is happening in real time. The device adopts a design, 6 non-brightness infrared infrared lamps, and a night vision distance of 5M. You can turn it on/off.

name: Blink Floodlight camera - Wireless smart security Outdoor camera (3rd Gen) + LED mount, two-year battery, motion detection - Add-on camera (Sync Module required) (Black)
feature_bullets: Blink Floodlight works with Outdoor to deliver a wire-free, HD smart security LED floodlight camera with up to two years of battery life.,See, hear, and speak to visitors in real time with 1080p HD live view and two-way audio from the app.,Light up the night — get 700 lumens of motion-triggered, high-quality LED lights.,Choose to save and share clips in the cloud with a free 30-day trial of the Blink Subscription Plan or locally with a Blink Sync Module and USB flash drive (each sold separately).,Customize motion detection zones, enable alerts, and set lights to trigger from the free Blink Home Monitor app on your smartphone.,Set up yourself in minutes — connect Outdoor to wifi and follow in-app instructions. Mount where you want with the included kit (hook included for no drill installation on vinyl siding).,Works with Alexa — use your voice to monitor your home with live view, motion alerts, and activate lights with select Alexa devices.,Includes Blink Outdoor camera, Floodlight mount, mounting bracket, two 1.5V AA lithium metal batteries, four D-Cell batteries, two mounting kits, and right angle adapter.

name: Blink Outdoor (3rd Gen) - wireless, weather-resistant HD security camera, two-year battery life, motion detection, set up in minutes – 3 camera system
feature_bullets: Blink Outdoor is a wireless battery-powered HD security camera that helps you monitor your home day or night with infrared night vision.,With long-lasting battery life, Outdoor runs for up to two years on two AA lithium batteries (included).,Store video clips and photos in the cloud with the Blink Subscription Plan and save events locally to the Blink Sync Module 2 via a USB flash drive (sold separately).,Outdoor is built to withstand the elements to help you protect your home inside or out, come rain or shine.,Designed so you can set up yourself in minutes. No wiring, no professional installation required.,Get motion detection alerts on your phone with the option to customize motion zones in the Blink Home Monitor app so you’re only alerted when you need to be.,See, hear, and speak to visitors with live view in real time and two-way audio features on your Blink app.,Works with Alexa – use your voice to monitor your home through supported Alexa-enabled devices.,Includes three Blink Outdoor cameras and one Sync Module 2.

name: Kasa 4MP 2K Security Camera Outdoor Wired, IP65, Starlight Sensor & 98 Ft Night Vision, Motion/Person Detection, 2-Way Audio w/Siren, Cloud/SD Card Storage, Alexa &Google Assistant Compatible(KC420WS)
feature_bullets: IP65 & 2K HD: Deploy your outdoor security camera with a true to its name weatherproof IP65. Pristine 4MP 2K video will capture every detail of what goes on outside your home, see every object someone is holding, recognize every face that passes by, no important details will be missed.Controller Type:Google Assistant;Amazon Alexa.Connectivity protocol:Wi-Fi.Power source type:Corded Electric,Starlight Sensor & Night Vision: With Starlight Sensor, images in low-light conditions will still appear crisp and high resolution. Determine if it’s just an animal rustling behind a bush or who that shady figure is across the street. Dual-integrated spotlights for colored night vision, to 98 ft.,Detection & Notification: Receive notifications that matter instantly thanks to the AI-powered algorithms. If there is motion or a person detected in the security camera's field of view, you'll but notified as soon as it happens. No more wondering when or if the package was delivered.,2-Way Audio w/ Built In Siren With high-quality microphone and speakers, 2-way talk quality is better than ever before. Activate push-to-talk anytime via the Kasa app. Additionally, ward off intruders with the built-in siren to protect your home from unwanted visitors.

name: Wireless Cameras for Home/Outdoor Security, Battery Powered 1080P HD WiFi Security Cameras Wireless Outdoor with Spotlight, AI Motion Detection, Color Night Vision, SD/Cloud-2 Pack
feature_bullets: 【Smart Motion Detection and AI Recognition】The rechargeable wireless outdoor security camera utilizes AI smart sensors, which can recognize people, pets, vehicles and package drop-offs. The security cameras wireless outdoor use an infrared sensor, it will detect motion and send notifications to your mobile phone in real-time.,【100% Wireless and Long Life Battery】The cameras for home security with a built-in rechargeable battery, it can provide 1 to 6 months of worry free use before a recharge is required. The outdoor camera wireless needn't any wires, the installation is very simple and it's waterproof, which can be installed in anywhere.,【1080P HD Live Video and Color Night Vision】This security camera provides 1080P quality video and image. It will automatically adjust to the ambient light level and when necessary. At night, it will auto-switch to color night vision effected of up to 33ft visible range, provides a wide clear vision.,【Two-Way Audio, Instant Siren, Spotlight】This wireless security camera outdoor has a built-in microphone and speaker, you can make 2-way audio calls in real-time. The instant siren, flashing white light and 2-way talk can drive away thieves and unwanted visitors.,【Cloud/SD & Free 3-Day Cycle Cloud Storage】The home security camera supports SD card and cloud storage. It provides free rolling 3-day cycled cloud storage that you can enjoy storage service without any subscription. And it provides a 30-day free trial of advanced features that include AI recognition, upgraded cloud memory, custom alert areas and etc, the advanced features starts at $2.99 per month after 30 days free trial.

NOTE: It does NOT SUPPORT PC or Macbook and Linux!,[ Easy to Use ] Download the "Aisee Pro" application, connect your phone via Wi-Fi, easily capture images or videos. No need for extra cable or adapter. And check the unknown situation inside ear canal, eardrum and check if plugged up, got infected as well as clean earwax completely in a quick and safe way.,[ Easy to Clean Ear Wax ] Perfect Ear Wax Removal Tool with 6 sizes of silicone ear picks are that included to aid in the comfortable removal of earwax without scratching. And 6 LED lights give the camera a perfect view of your inner ear.,[ 3.9MM Ultra-thin Otoscope ] With a diameter of 3.9MM can easily check the ear canal, eardrum, tympanum, mouth, gums, throat, nasal cavity and scalp hair roots from children over three years old, adults, pets. It is an essential tool for every family, classroom and pet hospital. PLEASE disinfect these speculums with alcohol or at 212℉ for 5 minutes after each use.,[ Fixed Focal Length ] A 1-inch (1~2.5cm) focal distance between the camera lens and your inner ear will give the sharpest images. Please make sure you adjust the correct distance between the probe and your ear to prevent blurry images. This also prevents injury, as it keeps the probe away from your delicate eardrum.

name: Boomph's Fujifilm Instax Mini Instant Film Kit: 20 Shoots Total, (10 Sheets x 2) - Capture Memories Anytime, Anywhere
feature_bullets: INSTAX COMPATIBILITY: Use our film with your Fujifilm Instax Mini cameras including the Mini 12, Mini 11, Mini 9, Mini 8, Mini 7+, Mini 40, Mini SP-2, Mini Link, Mini 90, Mini 70, Mini 40, Mini Hello Kitty, Polaroid PIC 300 and other Instant Film Cameras!,PREMIUM QUALITY: These Instax films are Hi-Speed ISO 800 so you can be sure they will capture your shots in the best light, giving you beautiful, natural looking colors with awesome grain quality.,CLEAR PHOTOS IN AN INSTANT: Snap a picture and immediately get a high res photo printed in seconds with your Fujifilm camera – photos are high quality with optimal grain quality.,MINI WALLET SIZED: Our white film sheets provide you with credit card sized photos (5.4 x 8.6 cm) for you to carry precious memories with you anywhere right in your bag or pocket!,PHOTOS THAT WILL LAST A LIFETIME: Using thin-film technology, images develop quicker! Using emulsion, development accelerators and control tech, your photos will last forever.

name: Digital Camera with Macro & Wide Angle Lens 48MP 4K Full HD Vlogging Camera for YouTube 3.0 Inch Screen Compact Camera for Beginners Teens Photography with Two Rechargeable Batteries
feature_bullets: [48MP & 4K HD Digital Camera] This new upgrade vlog camera with excellent performance shoot clear photos up to 48 megapixels and recording video resolution up to 4K/3840X2160. Supports 16X Digital Zoom(Focus Fixed). You can use this compact camera at anytime to capture and record the wonderful times you have with families and friends.,[Multifunctions Photography Camera] The photo camera has multiple functions including self-timer, Continuous Shooting, anti-shake, flash and more. Its flashlight system providing the best solution in dim light conditions. When your vision is limited in a dark environment, you can pop up the flash to get a brighter view.,[Webcam Function] The small camera support webcam function, it can be used as camera webcam by selecting the "PC Camera" mode after connected to your PC via the USB cable, you can have video calls or start live streaming to share things on social media. So its not only a photo camera for photography but also a streaming camera and video camera for Youtube, Instagram, etc.,[Long Time Recording Camera] The vlog camera contains two 1500mAh rechargeable batteries and supports recording while charging, makes it suitable for long-term shooting. This portable camera supports up to 128GB SD card (not included), so there is no need to worry about insufficient memory. Also, it contains extra MACRO lens and wide angle lens, makes photography more interesting.,[Perfect Gift for Beginners] The pocket camera has an exquisite looking, is perfect gift for entry-level users, the point and shoot camera is easy to operate. It is also an ideal gift for kids, friends and families. Recording travel, sports events, weddings, birthday parties and other activities will be so easy with its help. If you have any question about the product, please feel free to contact us.

name: Anchioo Instant Print Camera Toys for Toddlers Age 3-8,Boys and Girls Birthday Gifts with 1080P HD Video Recording,Kids Selfie Digital Camera Electronic Travel Game with Photo Paper 6 Color Pens,Blue
feature_bullets: 📸【Instant Print Camera for Kids】With instant imaging technology, Anchioo kids camera can print out a photo in one second.No ink cartridges or toners are needed.Just choose the photo mode and press the "shoot" button,a black & white picture will show on.Let’s take funny pictures with family and friends!,🎁【Adequate Print Papers Fantastic Frames】There are 3 rolls of print paper and up to shoot 372 pictures.It is a good toy camera choice for toddlers age 3-5.Our camera have 15 kinds of scene filters and 16 kinds of sticker.The package within 6 colorful pens.Boys and girls can take selfies or doodle pictures to show their imagination.,🌺【Multifunctional Toy Camera with Recording】This video camera support HD 1080P recording,with 2.4 inch large screen and 16X digital zoom,children can get a larger view to save the precious time.A 32G memory card installed in advance,which allows to store hundreds of photos.,⭐【Portable Camera 1000mAh Rechargeable Battery】Support 2.5 hours of continuous video after fully charge.Type-C USB charging is very convenient on the road trip.This mini digital camera is also equipped with a same color lanyard, easy for children to carry around.It is convenient to keep track of the life.,🎅【A Ideal Gift for Toddlers】The printing camera helps to record every meaningful moment of kids' childhood. It have 6 function mode,such as photo,video,music,playback,games,etc.Accompany children to explore the world for a long time.It is a great Birthday gifts,Christmas gifts for kids between 3-12 years old.

name: GNCC Pet Camera, Indoor Camera for Baby/Pet/Security with Night Vision, Dog Camera, 2-Way Audio, 2.4G WiFi, 360° PTZ Remote Control(Manual Up and Down), Smart Detection, SD&Cloud Storage, P1
feature_bullets: ✅ [Ultimate Smart Pet Camera] This pet camera has all the advanced features you want at an affordable price that's impossible to beat. Perfect for keeping an eye on every room in your home while you are at work, traveling, or at the beach. Phone app lets you control camera movements, listen, and talk no matter where you are,✅ [Impressive Clear View & Wide Angle] Features super clear 1080p, 6G lens, 2MP pixel. This pet camera lets you see the entire room with motion detection that follows the action. Now you can see and hear exactly what pets, kids, and intruders are doing. This is your best option for a cheap monitoring system,✅ [355 Degree Horizontal Rotation] This pet camera moves to cover everywhere you want to see. 105 degree vertical rotation so you can look up, down, right, and left with nothing out of view. This also offers two way communication so you can hear sounds and talk to people and pets on the other side,✅ [Powerful Night Vision] See clearly in low light conditions. Great for detecting night time wildlife, discover what pets are doing at night, and prevent intruders who break and enter after dark. It's makes a terrific pet cam that lets you look all around your little one's darkened room,✅ [Attention!!!]🦴 We provide 24H/7 support service. 🦴 The camera only supports APP left and right control, not remote control up and down. 🦴 Package includes complete wall-mounted accessories. 🦴 SD card is not included (64G TF card is recommended). 🦴 Only supports 2.4G WIFI, does not support 5G WIFI🦴

name: Kasa Smart 2023 New Indoor Pan-Tilt Security Camera, 1080p HD Dog Camera w/Night Vision, Motion Detection for Baby & Pet Monitor, Cloud & SD Card Storage, Works w/Alexa & Google Home, 2.4G WiFi (EC71)
feature_bullets: 【Up, Down, All Around】This Pan/Tilt IP camera see everything across an entire room or walkway with the 360° horizontal and 113° vertical range pan/tilt field of view. Set up the 【Patrol Mode】on EC71 to monitor each region at intervals of your choosing.,【Motion Tracking】Kasa Smart Hidden Camera with Audio/Video can automatically track moving objects or people, providing real-time alerts and increasing the overall effectiveness of your security system.,【Detection & Instant Notification】Get instant push notifications when motion or a person is detected, you can even enable baby crying detection to use EC71 as a baby camera monitor. Discern from notifications that matter, so you'll know if it’s your pet playing around or if someone is actually there.,【2-Way Audio w/ Built In Siren】Never truly leave home with the built-in 2-way audio. Use as a pet camera with phone app to comfort your pet from anywhere in the world. Keep your family safe with cameras for home security indoor by warding off intruders.,【Secure Local or Cloud Storage】Save footage continuously on up to a 256 GB microSD card (not included) or subscribe to Kasa Care for cloud storage which saves 30-day video history and provides additional benefits such as “Video Summary”, “Activity Notifications with Snapshots” and more.,【Night Vision up to 30 Ft.】Never miss a thing that goes on, even at night thanks to the integrated IR system on this indoor camera which provides 30 feet of night vision.,【1080P Full HD】Capture every detail inside your home with crystal-clear 1080P Full HD video with this indoor security camera. Easily see what your baby is holding or what your pet is playing with.,【Works w/ Alexa & Google Home】Fully compatible with Amazon Alexa and Google Home, use your simple voice command to view Kasa indoor security camera live stream on Echo Show or Google Chrome Cast with a screen.
